data.description: One and Half blocks form the NJ transit lightrail and easy access to all other public transportation. Eight blocks from NJ Turnpike Exit 14A. Close to Malls and Shopping Districts. Close to Liberty National Golf Course, Liberty Science Center and Liberty State Park. Ten Minutes to Holland Tunnel, Bayonne Bridge to Staten Island and NY Ferry.
data.whatILove: I love my neighbors! The access to transportation. The NJ transit light rail is two blocks away, many buses stop feet away. There is a diner around the block, stores, Costco 5 minutes away and a Walmart less than 15 minutes away. There is a mall 10 minutes away.
